items.badge_description: While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 270 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 55!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 450 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 91!
